---
layout: base.njk
title: L'Archive / Systems
description: Crawlable Forgotten Industries system browse index.
permalink: /archive/systems/
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---
<section class="masthead">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <p class="section-label">L'Archive / Systems</p>
    <h1>Systems</h1>
    <p class="tagline">Dossiers, restoration systems, field systems, operating layers, and object group contexts.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="source-band">
  <div class="section-inner band-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="section-label">{{ taxonomy.systems | count }} terms</p>
      <h2>Machines belong to systems.</h2>
    </div>

    <ul class="link-list archive-record-list">
      {% for term in taxonomy.systems %}
      <li>
        <p class="entry-note">{{ term.records.length }} record{% if term.records.length != 1 %}s{% endif %}</p>
        <h3><a href="{{ term.url }}">{{ term.label }}</a></h3>
      </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>
